 291                                    track.Rotations.Add(Quaternion.Slerp(track.Rotations[prevFrame], tempRotations[keyId
 292                                }
 293                                track.Rotations.Add(tempRotations[keyIdx]);
 294                                frameIdx = nextFrame;
 295                            }
 296                        }
 297                    }
 298                }
 299
 300                RawAnimationData.Add(track);
 301            }
 302            static float getW(float x, float y, float z)
 303            {
 304                float wSquared = 1.0f - (x * x + y * y + z * z);
 305                return (float)(wSquared > 0f ? Math.Sqrt(wSquared) : 0f);
 306            }
 307        }

 309        void CompressAnimationData(MEGame game, AnimationCompressionFormat newRotationCompression)
 310        {
 311            if (RawAnimationData is null)
 312            {
 313                DecompressAnimationData();
 314            }
 315
 316            keyEncoding = AnimationKeyFormat.AKF_ConstantKeyLerp;
 317            posCompression = AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_None;
 318            rotCompression = newRotationCompression;
 319            TrackOffsets = new int[Bones.Count * 4];
 320            var ms = new MemoryStream();
 321
 322            for (int i = 0; i < Bones.Count; i++)
 323            {
 324                AnimTrack track = RawAnimationData[i];
 325
 326                TrackOffsets[i * 4] = (int)ms.Position;
 327                int numPosKeys = track.Positions.Count;
 328                TrackOffsets[i * 4 + 1] = numPosKeys;
 329
 330                if (numPosKeys > 0)
 331                {
 332                    AnimationCompressionFormat compressionFormat = posCompression;
 333
 334                    if (numPosKeys == 1)
 335                    {
 336                        compressionFormat = AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_None;
 337                    }
 338
 339                    for (int j = 0; j < numPosKeys; j++)
 340                    {
 341                        switch (compressionFormat)
 342                        {
 343                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_None:
 344                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_Float96NoW:
 345                                ms.WriteFloat(track.Positions[j].X);
 346                                ms.WriteFloat(track.Positions[j].Y);
 347                                ms.WriteFloat(track.Positions[j].Z);
 348                                break;
 349                            default:
 350                                throw new NotImplementedException($"Translation keys in format {compressionFormat} canno
 351                        }
 352                    }
 353                    PadTo4();
 354                }
 355
 356                TrackOffsets[i * 4 + 2] = (int)ms.Position;
 357                int numRotKeys = track.Rotations.Count;
 358                TrackOffsets[i * 4 + 3] = numRotKeys;
 359
 360                if (numRotKeys > 0)
 361                {
 362                    AnimationCompressionFormat compressionFormat = rotCompression;
 363
 364                    if (numRotKeys == 1)
 365                    {
 366                        compressionFormat = AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_Float96NoW;
 367                    }
 368                    else if (game != MEGame.UDK)
 369                    {
 370                        float xMin, yMin, zMin, xMax, yMax, zMax;
 371                        xMin = yMin = zMin = float.MaxValue;
 372                        xMax = yMax = zMax = float.MinValue;
 373
 374                        foreach (Quaternion quat in track.Rotations)
 375                        {
 376                            xMin = Math.Min(xMin, quat.X);
 377                            yMin = Math.Min(yMin, quat.Y);
 378                            zMin = Math.Min(zMin, quat.Z);
 379                            xMax = Math.Max(xMax, quat.X);
 380                            yMax = Math.Max(yMax, quat.Y);
 381                            zMax = Math.Max(zMax, quat.Z);
 382                        }
 383
 384                        ms.WriteFloat(xMin);
 385                        ms.WriteFloat(yMin);
 386                        ms.WriteFloat(zMin);
 387                        ms.WriteFloat(xMax - xMin);
 388                        ms.WriteFloat(yMax - yMin);
 389                        ms.WriteFloat(zMax - zMin);
 390                    }
 391
 392                    for (int j = 0; j < numRotKeys; j++)
 393                    {
 394                        Quaternion rot = track.Rotations[j];
 395                        switch (compressionFormat)
 396                        {
 397                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_None:
 398                                ms.WriteFloat(rot.X);
 399                                ms.WriteFloat(rot.Y);
 400                                ms.WriteFloat(rot.Z);
 401                                ms.WriteFloat(rot.W);
 402                                break;
 403                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_Float96NoW:
 404                                ms.WriteFloat(rot.X);
 405                                ms.WriteFloat(rot.Y);
 406                                ms.WriteFloat(rot.Z);
 407                                break;
 408                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_BioFixed48:
 409                            {
 410                                const float shift = 0.70710678118f;
 411                                const float scale = 1.41421356237f;
 412                                const float precisionMult = 32767.0f;
 413                                //smallest three compression: https://gafferongames.com/post/snapshot_compression/
 414                                //omit the largest component, and store its index
 415                                int wPos = 0;
 416                                float max = 0f;
 417                                for (int k = 0; k < 4; k++)
 418                                {
 419                                    if (Math.Abs(rot[k]) > max)
 420                                    {
 421                                        max = Math.Abs(rot[k]);
 422                                        wPos = k;
 423                                    }
 424                                }
 425                                //remap the smallest three components to the lower 15 bits of a ushort
 426                                ushort a, b, c;
 427
 428                                static ushort compress(float f) => (ushort)((f + shift) / scale * precisionMult).Clamp(0
 429
 430                                switch (wPos)
 431                                {
 432                                    case 0:
 433                                        a = compress(rot.Y);
 434                                        b = compress(rot.Z);
 435                                        c = compress(rot.W);
 436                                        break;
 437                                    case 1:
 438                                        a = compress(rot.X);
 439                                        b = compress(rot.Z);
 440                                        c = compress(rot.W);
 441                                        break;
 442                                    case 2:
 443                                        a = compress(rot.X);
 444                                        b = compress(rot.Y);
 445                                        c = compress(rot.W);
 446                                        break;
 447                                    default:
 448                                        a = compress(rot.X);
 449                                        b = compress(rot.Y);
 450                                        c = compress(rot.Z);
 451                                        break;
 452                                }
 453
 454                                //stuff the 2 bit index of the omitted component into the high bits of a and b
 455                                a |= (ushort)((wPos & 2) << 14);
 456                                b |= (ushort)((wPos & 1) << 15);
 457
 458                                ms.WriteUInt16(a);
 459                                ms.WriteUInt16(b);
 460                                ms.WriteUInt16(c);
 461                            }
 462                                break;
 463                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_Fixed48NoW:
 464                            {
 465
 466                                const float scale = 32767.0f;
 467                                const ushort shift = 32767;
 468                                ms.WriteUInt16((ushort)(rot.X * scale + shift).Clamp(0, ushort.MaxValue));
 469                                ms.WriteUInt16((ushort)(rot.Y * scale + shift).Clamp(0, ushort.MaxValue));
 470                                ms.WriteUInt16((ushort)(rot.Z * scale + shift).Clamp(0, ushort.MaxValue));
 471                                break;
 472                            }
 473                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_IntervalFixed32NoW:
 474                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_Fixed32NoW:
 475                            case AnimationCompressionFormat.ACF_Float32NoW:
 476                            default:
 477                                throw new NotImplementedException($"Rotation keys in format {compressionFormat} cannot b
 478                        }
 479                    }
 480                    PadTo4();
 481                }
 482            }
 483
 484            CompressedAnimationData = ms.ToArray();
 485            compressedDataSource = game;
 486

 488            void PadTo4()
 489            {
 490                var numAlignBytes = ms.Position.Align(4) - ms.Position;
 491                for (int j = 0; j < numAlignBytes; j++)
 492                {
 493                    ms.WriteByte(0x55);
 494                }
 495            }
 496        }
 497    }

 401                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionConstant":

 403                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionFmod":

 407                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionFoldedMath":
 408                    return new MaterialUniformExpressionFoldedMath();
 409                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionTime":
 410                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionRealTime":
 411                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionFractionOfEffectEnabled":
 412                    return new MaterialUniformExpression();
 413                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionScalarParameter":
 414                    return new MaterialUniformExpressionScalarParameter();
 415                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionSine":

 417                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionTexture":

 420                case "FMaterialUniformExpressionTextureParameter":
